Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我现在想去小千家 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现...现在？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是学校祭的准备？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化装游行的...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.54,0:07:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化装？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家送了江米条 拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江米条？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.57,0:08:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.95,0:08:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校祭啊 我高中的时候还帮忙制作酱汁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.33,0:08:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在模拟的小吃店里帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.06,0:08:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲣节和海带 干蘑菇和干海参
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.55,0:08:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 是那些东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用锯切干香菇真难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.66,0:08:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶...听上去很好味的酱汁 酱汁？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻轻地 轻轻地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷下去了 陷下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬起来 抬起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得 花车是不能弄出学校的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我们过去吧 阿痞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管哪个班都这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.44,0:08:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:08:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是班主任啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.81,0:08:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啥 反正我不关心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不关心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是班主任
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.61,0:09:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 你们可别被其老师发现了 会很麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是过了一关
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.49,0:09:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬起那边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.31,0:09:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你这么过分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.73,0:09:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候变成那样的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.19,0:09:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天那样的表现让人以为你有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个可怕的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还摆出一张人畜无害的脸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.43,0:09:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把黑沼甩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全被你骗过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.19,0:09:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你那么焦急地是去甩一个女生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你将来想当什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情夫吗 牛郎吗 还是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.56,0:09:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你应该是特地跑过去拒绝她的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这样说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 风早？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被阿痞抓住了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.74,0:10:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 你们先走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.23,0:10:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是去告白的 但是没成功
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.46,0:10:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 是那么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.72,0:10:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只说了些不痛不痒的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真废柴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把该说的话都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.16,0:10:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了 别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你虽然说什么「不了解黑沼」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上 你光是整理自己的头绪已经缓不过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样有什么不好 放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 真奇怪 对不上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.82,0:11:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.73,0:11:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 应该这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.33,0:11:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我多管闲事了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.97,0:11:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.21,0:11:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank You 贞子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.42,0:12:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小千
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.65,0:12:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发邮件给我 叫我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 放学后...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都有我们这样的朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算要自我贬低着活多久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.69,0:12:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年 我能跟小千绫音好好相处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是第一次有了跟别人亲近的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.22,0:13:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说...说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.17,0:13:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 别忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 去拿饮料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不就好了 爽子几句话就让她心情大好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几句话？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为我的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我确确实实向他传达了自己的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确凿无误地传达给他了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心意 传达到了么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.03,0:13:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传达给风早同学了么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡...胡桃 早...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.92,0:14:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一副「真是看错你了」的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.07,0:14:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贞子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,师傅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是...昨天...昨天让你看到我的丑态了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 应该说...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.63,0:14:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 你干的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找爽子什么事 别靠近她 一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.29,0:14:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是跟你说别多管闲事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.70,0:14:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都干了什么好事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 贞子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能风早真的是喜欢贞子你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:01.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这大嘴巴都说什么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,误...误会 不是的不是的 那是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「喜欢」的意义不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:33.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是贞子在否定她和风早的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早 龙 你们真慢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都集合...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 好像很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.21,0:15:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在不是很糟糕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.93,0:15:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你闭嘴就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.22,0:15:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:15:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.87,0:16:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花车能赶出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.26,0:16:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.41,0:16:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概前一天要通宵了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也要！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 果然是假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是连招呼都没打就走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这句话不知道当不当说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我觉得你可能没表达清楚自己的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去 应该再没法跟风早同学搭上话了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.43,0:16:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能一直注视着他的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连道早安也做不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:04.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许他再也不会笑着对我说「早上好」了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.41,0:17:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许他会回避我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候 是风早同学在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是风早同学向我搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了什么不该说的话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是「说了吗」的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要缝起来么 把你那大嘴巴给缝起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.20,0:17:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不好办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 我基本上还算个老实人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开 碍着人了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你们到别的地方解决好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来后来怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是问我关于贞子和风早的修罗场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.27,0:18:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡桃 你不是又有什么企图了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:22.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没对爽子做了什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.30,0:18:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.71,0:18:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骂了她一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教训一个情人节连巧克力都没送出的废人几句有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.30,0:18:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 为什么干那种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 胡桃是你干的好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.94,0:18:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 是我在从中作梗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这又有什么问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.95,0:18:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没送出去不是爽子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.16,0:18:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没跟她说过「别送」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8F55DF&\3c&HE4C4FE&\shad0\pos(454,147)}胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.43,0:18:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:18:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从中作梗是她不对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.08,0:19:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 胡桃也喜欢风早吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太大声了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.63,0:19:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 真头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我跟贞子交往的话 不正合胡桃的心意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.11,0:19:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是要妨碍她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想承认自己输给了那种女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到她是那么没劲的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太让我失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.29,0:19:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡桃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风早果然是喜欢贞子的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.19,0:20:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不能放着不管吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.62,0:20:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是为了贞子...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.83,0:20:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了爽子？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了你自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.65,0:20:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了「我是好人」这种自我满足
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为了把自己打造成一个大善人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.47,0:20:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让爽子遭受了多么难过的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.69,0:20:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围有什么闲言碎语她就会钻牛角尖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再管这事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没看清吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从来没有主动去做过什么
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======预告=======
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.02,0:22:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想传达出去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 就想告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.25,0:22:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话 传达
